s a director of axiall corporation nyse axll and tronox incorporated nyse trox mr gervis holds a bs in industrial engineering from lehigh university and a jd from the george washington university mr gervis also is a cfa charter holder the board has concluded that mr gervis possesses specific attributes that qualify him to serve as a member of our board of directors including his extensive experience in finance capital markets and investing his management skills as well as his experience with sophisticated transactions as a corporate attorney in addition because mr gervis has served on many boards of directors the board has concluded that he has substantial experience regarding how boards can and should effectively oversee and manage companies and a significant understanding of governance issues source aspen aerogels on    sign up for equilar atlas and view robert m gerviss full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like robert m gervis more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in robert m gerviss network and community follow changes in robert m gerviss employment and moneyinmotion connect with robert m gervis through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example robert m gervis robert m gerviss connections  sign up now to view robert m gerviss  connections » gregory c thompson executive vice president and chief financial officer axiall corporation thomas j casey chairman of the board tronox limited michael j foster senior vice president general counsel and secretary lsb industries inc peter johnston director and interim chief executive officer tronox limited gregory d blue board member tronox limited andrew p hines board member tronox limited sipho a nkosi board member tronox limited katherine c harper executive vice president and chief financial officer agrofresh solutions inc stephen e macadam dir president and chief